#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral\\_chisquare"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a noncentral chi-square distribution."
msgstr "从非中心卡方分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:3 of
msgid ""
"The noncentral :math:`\\chi^2` distribution is a generalisation of the "
":math:`\\chi^2` distribution."
msgstr "非中心 :math:`\\chi^2` 分布是 :math:`\\chi^2` 分布的推广。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:6 of
msgid "Degrees of freedom, should be > 0."
msgstr "自由度，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:8 of
msgid "Non-centrality, should be non-negative."
msgstr "非中心性，应为非负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:10 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``df`` and ``nonc`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``mt.broadcast(df, nonc).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``df`` 和 ``nonc`` 均为标量，则返回单个"
"值。否则，抽取 ``mt.broadcast(df, nonc).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:15 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:17 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配到 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:19 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:22 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized noncentral chi-square "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的非中心卡方分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:27 of
msgid ""
"The probability density function for the noncentral Chi-square "
"distribution is"
msgstr "非中心卡方分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:30 of
msgid ""
"P(x;df,nonc) = \\sum^{\\infty}_{i=0}\n"
"\\frac{e^{-nonc/2}(nonc/2)^{i}}{i!}\n"
"\\P_{Y_{df+2i}}(x),\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "where :math:`Y_{q}` is the Chi-square with q degrees of freedom."
msgstr "其中 :math:`Y_{q}` 是具有 q 个自由度的卡方分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:36 of
msgid ""
"In Delhi (2007), it is noted that the noncentral chi-square is useful in "
"bombing and coverage problems, the probability of killing the point "
"target given by the noncentral chi-squared distribution."
msgstr ""
"Delhi (2007) 指出，非中心卡方分布在轰炸和覆盖问题中非常有用，点目标被摧毁"
"的概率由非中心卡方分布给出。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:42 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:43 of
msgid ""
"Delhi, M.S. Holla, \"On a noncentral chi-square distribution in the "
"analysis of weapon systems effectiveness\", Metrika, Volume 15, Number 1 "
"/ December, 1970."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:46 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Noncentral chi-square distribution\" "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noncentral_chi-square_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:50 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:51 of
msgid "Draw values from the distribution and plot the histogram"
msgstr "从分布中抽取值并绘制直方图"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:59 of
msgid ""
"Draw values from a noncentral chisquare with very small noncentrality, "
"and compare to a chisquare."
msgstr "从非中心性非常小的非中心卡方分布中抽取值，并与卡方分布进行比较。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_chisquare.noncentral_chisquare:70 of
msgid ""
"Demonstrate how large values of non-centrality lead to a more symmetric "
"distribution."
msgstr "演示较大的非中心性如何导致分布更加对称。"

